title: Greg Rutkowski Was Removed From Stable Diffusion, But AI Artists Brought Him Back
description: More popular than Picasso and Leonardo Da Vinci among AI artists, Greg Rutkowski opted out of the Stable Diffusion training set. The community just created a LoRA to mimic his style.

title: Wall Street banks back Elizabeth Warren’s Digital Asset Anti-Money Laundering Act
description:
U.S. senator Elizabeth Warren reintroduced the Digital Asset Anti-Money Laundering Act on July 28, backed by unlikely allies — the Wall Street banks. The Bank Policy Institute, a financial policy think tank made up of a cohort of banks, backed the legislation that aims to mitigate the national security risks posed by cryptocurrencies.
